29
00:01:49,926 --> 00:01:53,044
- I'm hoping it will work, yes.
- But, uh...

30
00:01:55,065 --> 00:01:58,867
They wouldn't operate unless it were
safe for the baby. Dr. Montgomery?

31
00:01:58,969 --> 00:02:02,888
Your blood pressure's high, but I'll
be there to monitor you and the baby.

32
00:02:02,990 --> 00:02:05,623
Get some rest.
We'll see you soon.

33
00:02:05,725 --> 00:02:09,327
- Thank you for staying.
- Least I could do for saving
Archie.

34
00:02:09,429 --> 00:02:12,164
Um...

35
00:02:12,266 --> 00:02:14,733
I know what we said
before about the baby,

36
00:02:14,835 --> 00:02:20,005
but if something should happen, if it
comes down to a choice, save my wife.

37
00:02:20,107 --> 00:02:23,408
We can make another baby.
We can't make another her.

38
00:02:28,331 --> 00:02:30,665
Fifty-two-year-old
male, fell down stairs.

39
