61
00:03:49,296 --> 00:03:54,116
- Coffee. Why, thank you, Mark.
- That's not for you either.

62
00:03:54,218 --> 00:03:58,787
- Good morning, Dr. Grey.
- Keep your secret coffee.

63
00:03:58,906 --> 00:04:02,691
Until you tell Derek, our
relationship continues to consist

64
00:04:02,793 --> 00:04:05,626
of you hiding in the attic and
me smuggling snacks past Mer.

65
00:04:05,729 --> 00:04:08,079
- Know what that makes you?
- Your boyfriend?

66
00:04:08,181 --> 00:04:11,967
Anne Frank. I'm dating
Anne Frank, and I'm tired of it.

67
00:04:12,069 --> 00:04:15,420
I want to go downstairs. I wanna
tell the Germans to kiss my ass.

68
00:04:15,522 --> 00:04:18,339
