69
00:04:18,441 --> 00:04:20,208
When I do, you'll be
my date to the wedding.

70
00:04:20,310 --> 00:04:23,644
- Derek proposed?
- Not yet. But when he does.

71
00:04:27,734 --> 00:04:30,535
This is the first step
in the start of a new life.

72
00:04:30,637 --> 00:04:32,937
How are we feeling?
Positive? Confident?

73
00:04:33,039 --> 00:04:35,440
I am good. Great.

74
00:04:35,542 --> 00:04:37,937
You take care of
your own feelings.

75
