my entire day around newborns.

219
00:13:36,949 --> 00:13:39,850
So I try not to in
my personal life.

220
00:13:39,952 --> 00:13:43,921
Thanks for asking,
though. I'm super flattered.

221
00:13:44,024 --> 00:13:45,823
Super.

222
00:13:51,831 --> 00:13:54,866
- As discussed.
- Thank you.

223
00:13:58,938 --> 00:14:02,172
Newborn. I'm not a newborn.

224
00:14:02,274 --> 00:14:05,243
I'm a senior resident.
I'm a great surgeon.

225
00:14:05,345 --> 00:14:07,512
I'm a divorcee, for God's sake.

226
00:14:07,614 --> 00:14:09,446
I'm...

227
00:14:09,549 --> 00:14:14,118
I'm, uh... looking for you to
agree with me here, Bailey.

228
00:14:14,921 --> 00:14:17,472
- Bailey?
- The chief,

229
00:14:17,574 --> 00:14:19,974
he wrote me a form
letter of recommendation.

230
00:14:20,076 --> 00:14:22,410
That's insane. He's
chief, you're Bailey.

231
00:14:22,512 --> 00:14:25,963
"Pleasant in the OR and
enjoyed by the nurses.

